<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Event Hub</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Event Hub</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#upcoming-events">Upcoming Events</a></li>
                <li><a href="#past-events">Past Events</a></li>
            <ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="upcoming-events">
            <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>

            <article>
                <h3>Community Picnic</h3>
                <p>Join friends and neighbors for a fun afternoon of food, games, and
          live music at the city park. Date: August 10, 2026. </p> 
          </article>
          <article>
            <h3>Tech Workshops</h3>
            <p>
            Learn the basics of HTML and CSS in this beginner-friendly workshop.
          Date: September 5, 2026.
            </p>
          </article>
        </section>

        <section id="past-events">
            <h2>Past Events</h2>
            <article>
                <h3>Spring Festival</h3>
                <p>Families enjoyed local food vendors, crafts, and outdoor activities
          during our annual spring celebration.
                </p>
                <img
                    src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/past-event1.jpg"
          alt="People enjoying the Spring Festival"
        >
      </article>

      <article>
        <h3>Charity Run</h3>
        <p>
          Hundreds of participants joined together to raise money for local
          charities in our annual community run.
        </p>
        <img
          src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/past-event2.jpg"
          alt="Participants running in the Charity Run"
        >
      </article>

    </section>

  </main>


</body>

</html>
